title._content: Catalogue of Books, Deseronto Public Library (1896), back cover

description._content: Back cover of the 1896 catalogue of books in Deseronto Public Library, Deseronto, Ontario, advertising "John McCullough, Insurance, Real Estate and Loan Agent. Appraiser for the Canada Permament [Permanent] Loan and Savings Company. Special Agent, Sec.-Treasurer and Valuator for the Provincial Building and Loan Association. Rents & Accounts Collected. Conveyancer, and Commissioner for taking Affidavits. Money to Loan at Lowest Rates of continuing the listing of Class M (Miscellaneous) and with an advertisement for the "Canadian Interest. Office: St. George Street, Deseronto, Ont."
